OL,3,CCoin found in house clearance sells
OL,4,Cfor six figure sum
OL,6,FAn "extremely rare" Victorian coin has
OL,7,Fbeen sold for #110,000 at auction
OL,8,Fafter being discovered during a house
OL,9,Fclearance in Gwynedd.
OL,11,FIt reached the six figure sum after it
OL,12,Fwent under the hammer at an auction in
OL,13,FChester on Thursday 9 April.
OL,15,FThe auction company, Rogers Jones,
OL,16,Festimated that only 300 - 500 of these
OL,17,Fcoins had been produced with the
OL,18,Fauction generating "worldwide
OL,19,Finterest".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
