OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776175862
OL,3,CCoin found in house clearance sells
OL,4,Cfor six figure sum
OL,6,FCharles Hampshire, who is a jewellery,
OL,7,Fcoins and watches specialist said the
OL,8,Fcoins unusual discovery location was
OL,9,Flike "discovering a diamond in hiding"
OL,11,FWhen originally created the coins were
OL,12,Fnot for general circulation and and
OL,13,Fhave remained "incredibly scarce" for
OL,14,Ftwo decades seen mostly in "high end
OL,15,Fcollector sets".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
