CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776175862
OL,3,CCoin found in house clearance sells
OL,4,Cfor six figure sum
OL,6,FThe coin was originally designed in
OL,7,F1839 to commemorate the anniversary of
OL,8,Fthe monarchs crowning and made history
OL,9,Fas the first time a person or monarch
OL,10,Fhad been featured on a coin as a
OL,11,Ffictional character.
OL,13,FNamed 'Una and the Lion,' the keepsake
OL,14,Fdesigned by the Royal Mint's chief
OL,15,Fengraver at the time, William Wyon and
OL,16,Fthe design is regarded as his
OL,17,F"crowning achievement".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
