PN,46904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776175862
OL,3,CCoin found in house clearance sells
OL,4,Cfor six figure sum
OL,6,FIt features an engraving of a young
OL,7,FQueen Victoria on one side, while the
OL,8,Fother side depicts her as the
OL,9,Fcharacter 'Una' from Edmund Spenser's
OL,10,Fpoem 'The Faerie Queene'.
OL,12,FThe design shows her guiding a lion,
OL,13,Fsaid to symbolize "her poise and the
OL,14,Fstrength of the British nation under
OL,15,Fher leadership".
OL,17,FThe mix of history, culture and art in
OL,18,Fthe coins story is, according to
OL,19,Fauctioneers what makes it "a "holy
OL,20,Fgrail" for numismatists".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
