OL,3,CCoin found in house clearance sells
OL,4,Cfor six figure sum
OL,6,FThe auction company described the
OL,7,Funique design as reflecting the
OL,8,F"optimism and energy of its period."
OL,9,Fcalling it a "real work of art in its
OL,10,Fown right".
